<doc id="1891" url="http://witcher.fandom.com/wiki?curid=1891" title="Kaer Morhen">
Kaer Morhen

"Do you really wish to know?" — Spoilers from the books and/or adaptations to follow!
&lt;infobox&gt;
 &lt;title source="name"&gt;&lt;default&gt;Kaer Morhen&lt;/default&gt;&lt;/title&gt;
 &lt;image source="image" /&gt;
