&lt;/infobox&gt;
The Ghoul Contract
"I need the blood of at least three ghouls. Will pay handsomely."
"Kalkstein, alchemist"
Walkthrough.
You will encounter ghouls while doing the quest for Mikul. Since there are not many ghouls in Chapter I, be sure to unlock the Ghoul bestiary entry before venturing into the crypt. After you have finished Mikul's quest there is a new passage in the crypt where you encounter more ghouls and a named alghoul. Every night there is also a ghoul which feasts on some corpses at the abandoned houses north of the cave. Collect three vials of ghoul blood and return to Kalkstein who resides at the local inn.
Phases.
Ghoul Blood.
Kalkstein the alchemist will pay for the blood of three ghouls. "I must collect the blood of three ghouls for Kalkstein."
Loot.
I have enough ghoul blood. It's time to see Kalkstein and collect my reward. "I should see Kalkstein and collect my reward."
Payment.
Kalkstein is using the blood in some of his research. Interesting... In any case, job done. "I received my reward for the ghoul blood." (100 + 3000 XP + Basics of Alchemy)

